Articles.Content:
I am currently building a space station and I am looking for some parts mods, I have wandered around SpacePort and found some great looking modules like Kosmos, Fustek and the like, however I don't like their appearance(Kosmos being too dark and Fustek being low textured) and I haven't found many good looking modules that fit the Stock Parts, This is the best i can find, called ExPI: Space Stations. But it is not updated anymore.

Any Suggestions? Space Station parts?
